<P><HI>The Remedies this little</HI> Tract <HI>pre&s;cribes, are &s;imple, a <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> obtained; and never fail of a</HI> Cure <HI>where the</HI> Di&s;order is cur|able: <HI>therefore no Man who values his</HI> Hor&s;e <HI>&s;hould pre&s;ume to travel with|out it.</HI></P>
